00:37:34.260 --> 00:37:42.010
the leader of the bee club and I, got the
bees out and put them into my hive. So, they

00:37:42.010 --> 00:37:46.801
were taken out. That's what we typically do,
is we rescue bees. People call and say, "I

00:37:46.801 --> 00:37:52.400
have a bee invasion." And we'll take those
bees and give them to people who want to put

00:37:52.400 --> 00:37:56.160
them into hives. People decorate their hives.

00:37:56.160 --> 00:37:58.250
[Pause]

00:37:58.250 --> 00:38:05.970
I'll skip that video. This is the only place
